{
  "stem": "24242.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Those are people, very few in a country like America, not only Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "For some reason or another, he went in on a turf fight with my brother Zisl.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother Zisl grabbed a baseball bat.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he said, your steel is not going to help you.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he gave in-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm giving you an example what kind of a man-- you asked me what kind of a man they-- they were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Zisl was a hot-head.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He would-- hit first and ask questions later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Tuvia was a much more conservative-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He would think twice before to hurt anyone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] But the most unique man-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I would say had to be Asael.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I don't know why it worked out how it worked out, but he was the-- the main man in the family, even as far as I can remember to 1940, 1939, '38.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Below that, I wouldn't remember anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was the main man in the family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was a man without a heart, a very good person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And my personal opinion is that-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he-- he was the power.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He was the strength of those three brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Zisl and him was like twins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Asael was somewhat older, about a year and a half from Zisl.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But Zisl would listen to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "No one in the family would ever contradict Asael.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And for some reason or another, the Gentile world knew there is more brothers than Asael and Zisl.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But if you will talk to them, Tuvia is older.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He would come later on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The main two that they were afraid of was Asael and Zisl.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
